statements: SELECT * FROM printing_materials_inventory;
SELECT id, material_name FROM printing_materials_inventory ORDER BY material_name DESC;
SELECT material_type, SUM(remaining_quantity) AS total_quantity FROM printing_materials_inventory GROUP BY material_type;
SELECT * FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE remaining_quantity > 50;
SELECT material_name, material_type FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE material_type = 'Paper';
SELECT * FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE material_type = 'paper' ORDER BY remaining_quantity DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT material_name, remaining_quantity FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE material_type = 'ink' ORDER BY material_name
SELECT id, material_name, material_type, remaining_quantity FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE remaining_quantity < 100 ORDER BY material_name ASC, remaining_quantity DESC
SELECT * FROM printing_materials_inventory WHERE material_type IN ('paper', 'ink') ORDER BY material_type, material_name
SELECT material_name, SUM(remaining_quantity) AS total_quantity FROM printing_materials_inventory GROUP BY material_name HAVING total_quantity > 500 ORDER BY total_quantity DESC

SELECT printers.model, printers.brand, print_jobs.start_time FROM printers JOIN print_jobs ON printers.id = print_jobs.printer_id WHERE print_jobs.quantity >= 10 ORDER BY print_jobs.start_time ASC;
SELECT resins.name, resins.type, print_jobs.quantity FROM resins JOIN print_jobs ON resins.id = print_jobs.resin_id WHERE resins.quantity < 50 ORDER BY print_jobs.quantity DESC;

SELECT filaments.name, filaments.quantity, printers.model FROM filaments JOIN print_jobs ON filaments.id = print_jobs.filament_id JOIN printers ON printers.id = print_jobs.printer_id WHERE print_jobs.end_time IS NOT NULL ORDER BY filaments.quantity ASC, printers.model DESC;

SELECT filament_name, filament_type, filament_price FROM filaments WHERE filament_type = 'PLA' ORDER BY filament_price DESC;
SELECT r.resin_name, r.resin_color, i.quantity FROM resins r JOIN inventory i ON r.resin_id = i.material_id WHERE i.quantity > 20;
